{"tid":2004603,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】POLYU手足爭取成功","createTime":"2020-05-06T14:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T04:21:09.000Z","uid":244005,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cd920bf91e746ed49a1d3ae7bfd3241f32b47c0c","tid":2004603,"uid":244005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:13:55.000Z","msg":"話說前排有手足揭發polyu學校諗住比大陸仔8月考 本地生就5月考 完sem就要即刻考<br />\n<br />\n經過手足不停遊說同爭取<br />\n<br />\nDear Students <br />\n  <br />\nSubsequent to the issuance of the Notice on Response Actions for the Novel Coronavirus (28) by the Chairman of the Task Force on the Delivery of Online Teaching on 22 April 2020, the University has received feedback from some PolyU students expressing their concerns on the perceived unfairness to have two examination periods for on-campus invigilated examinations for different groups of students.  As some students are not currently in Hong Kong and there are physical limitations for these students to come back and take the invigilated examinations in May, a number of examinations have been arranged to have examinations in May as well as in August to ensure all students are able to take the required examinations.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">終於成功</span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n廢話唔多講<br />\n<br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8355c1b74f9d4c3e697fd591a3cb13ef86f1152b","tid":2004603,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:14:45.000Z","msg":"特朗普真係落台啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2004593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2004593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2e931e51f67ada25104b57db5593e6ad7dd6e6a5","tid":2004603,"uid":156734,"li